room_title: Escape room "The Tiki Bar" by Perplexcity in Warren
room_description: Welcome to the Sunken Coconut. The owner of this eyesore is a man named Charles Keanu. Charles just finished having this upscale dive bar remodeled and is ready to reopen his doors. The only thing he has forgotten is where he left the WiFi password he needs to set up his PayPal account. The bar opens in an hour, help Charles find the password before the day drunks come in!
